{"tid":2418162,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"股神 Michael Burry：Bitcoin將被摧毀   通脹爆發各國需維護本國貨幣","createTime":"2021-02-22T11:55:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T18:30:05.000Z","uid":51620,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3675b660306c302106a38b76c855c6acbac0d2df","tid":2418162,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T11:55:31.000Z","msg":"電影《沽注一擲》的真人真事主角 Michael Burry ，在 2008 年憑著洞悉金融海嘯，一夜暴富成名，其公司更在前年大手買入  GME 股票勁賺42億港元。日前，他在 Twitter 發文指，美國經濟重啟、推出更多經濟刺激方案將推高通脹，目前至少負債 3 美元才能達到 1 美元國內生產總值 GDP，各國政府可能會「摧毀」比特幣及黃金，從而保障當地的貨幣。<br />\n<br />\n據外媒報導，知名對沖基金經理人 Michael Burry 曾在2月18日已刪除的推文指，經濟刺激方案正在啟動，早在 COVID-19 來襲前，每負債 3 美元才能創造 1 美元 GDP，如今情況更惡化。若通脹危機爆發，各國政府將會摧毀法定貨幣競爭者，例如比特幣、黃金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/02/22/michael-burry-bitcoin/fun-tech/?fbclid=IwAR2sh7RsVjGLNccvGfHDp7h1BBB2vgdnynAqeUibVYY-PkoT2GCyP55LOgU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F02%2F22%2Fmichael-burry-bitcoin%2Ffun-tech%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2sh7RsVjGLNccvGfHDp7h1BBB2vgdnynAqeUibVYY-PkoT2GCyP55LOgU&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XhR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=7b8b9056\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/02/22/michael-burry-bitcoin/fun-tech/?fbclid=IwAR2sh7RsVjGLNccvGfHDp7h1BBB2vgdnynAqeUibVYY-PkoT2GCyP55LOgU</a>"},{"pid":"6b40ca141c86a1e10c7c25103f5270a7691b1520","tid":2418162,"uid":194076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T11:57:49.000Z","msg":"OK， 上１０萬"},{"pid":"adc295048dfd67b8fa1e13f8f1c141b146a3fb16","tid":2418162,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T11:58:43.000Z","msg":"幾年前已經聽過"},{"pid":"66bfaa7eb0df036c62ce8040370cdb912dd8e054","tid":2418162,"uid":30067,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T12:01:39.000Z","msg":"Bitcoin 就係各國既貨幣"},{"pid":"060e9654180ac5f39add76ede359ea38ff669083","tid":2418162,"uid":54884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T12:0